graph LR
    TrainingOp[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>v1.9.0]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    TrainingOp -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.27+]
    TrainingOp -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19.1]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano v1.9.0<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins v0.28.9<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|cert mgmt| ExternalCertMgr[External cert-manager<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Built-in components
    TrainingOp -->|uses internally| CertController[cert-controller<br/>open-policy-agent]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    TrainingOp -->|deployed by| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>Internal RHOAI]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI mgmt| TrainingOp
    Notebooks[RHOAI Notebooks] -.->|submits jobs| TrainingOp
    DataPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|pipeline tasks| TrainingOp

    %% Kubernetes Components
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>CRUD operations]
    K8sAPI -->|creates| Pods[Training Pods]
    K8sAPI -->|creates| Services[Services]
    K8sAPI -->|creates| ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]
    K8sAPI -->|creates| HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]
    K8sAPI -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies]

    %% CRDs Managed
    subgraph CRDs["Custom Resources (kubeflow.org/v1)"]
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob]
        TFJob[TFJob]
        XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob]
        MPIJob[MPIJob]
        JAXJob[JAXJob]
        PaddleJob[PaddleJob]
    end

    TrainingOp -->|watches/reconciles| CRDs

